    "stat_block": {
        "type": "stat_block",
        "subtype": "siege_weapon",
        "text": "Orcs of Belkzen pioneered the invention of this siege engine, which merges the concepts of battering ram and catapult. A large stone block, one end honed to be like the engine\u2019s namesake wolf fang, is attached to a wooden arm that can be winched back. When the lever is pulled, the arm swings the block forward with great force, the stone piercing almost any object directly ahead of it.",
